      <h2>Our Platform – Frozen Forward Agenda</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Mental Health Awareness:</strong> Destigmatize mental health and expand access to support services.</li>
        <li><strong>Accessible Education & Healthcare:</strong> Universal access to education and quality healthcare for all citizens.</li>
        <li><strong>Civic Engagement:</strong> Increase voter participation and civic education for young people.</li>
        <li><strong>Equality & Social Justice:</strong> Fight systemic discrimination and promote civil rights protections.</li>
        <li><strong>LGBTQ+ Rights:</strong> Defend and advance the rights of LGBTQ+ individuals everywhere.</li>
        <li><strong>Climate Action:</strong> Tackle global warming with clean energy and international climate cooperation.</li>
      </ul>
